reviewText: Would not play on my DVD player.
A very interesting film. It should be enjoyed by lovers of history, Hebrew bible and those interested in archeology. Did I forget treasure hunters? Yes , those too!

This is unfortunately a documentary that involved Vendyl Jones, a right wing copper scroll nutcase.  There are some well thought out documentaries on the copper scroll, but this isn't one of them.  Please stay clear of it, and find another.
